                    <head type="stepTitle" xml:lang="en">Selection of texts to gather in a research corpus</head>
                    
                    <desc type="definition" xml:lang="en">Based on the project's bibiography it is advised to search for existing digital resources which might be reused in the current research context. Browsing for digital resources might be perfomed on different platforms, e.g. VLO, Europeana, German Digital Library (for German resources). The primary goal here would be to find digitized full-texts of reliable versions of the works in consideration. However, if digitized full-texts are not available, text recognition has to be considered. For that, the current step may also include a search for digital images of the written records (Europeana, VD, KVK) to be used as a basis for text recognition.</desc>
                    <desc xml:lang="en" type="terms">
                      <term type="activity" source="http://tadirah.dariah.eu/" key="Discovering"/>
                    	<term type="activity" source="http://tadirah.dariah.eu/" key="Gathering"/>
                    	<term type="technique" source="http://tadirah.dariah.eu/" key="Browsing"/>
                    	<term type="technique" source="http://tadirah.dariah.eu/" key="Searching"/>
                    	<term type="object" source="http://tadirah.dariah.eu/" key="Text"/>
                    	<term type="object" source="http://tadirah.dariah.eu/" key="Metadata"/>
                    	<term type="object" source="http://tadirah.dariah.eu/" key="Images"/>
                    </desc>
                	
